  "detailed_description": "《客栈江湖》，带着江湖风味的经营类游戏，而你扮演一名在江湖中寂寂无名的客栈掌柜。<br>你需要不断的接待客人，获取铜钱，派临时雇员去四处为你探索收集食谱与食材。在夜晚培养你的厨师，研究与学习菜谱，提升客栈在江湖中的名声，吸引更多的客人到来。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383500/extras/1e69c84e829a5fb2545eef1e4fee8e5f.poster.avif?t=1597647957\" width=71 height=103 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383500/extras/1e69c84e829a5fb2545eef1e4fee8e5f.webm?t=1597647957\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>初期只是一个小客栈，当拥有足够的金钱和名声时，可以对客栈进行升级，获得更多的座位以及厨师岗位。通过固定时间段的比赛，最终成为名扬四海的客栈。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383500/extras/5dc89dc68162e3f81d217562c4927d67.poster.avif?t=1597647957\" width=71 height=103 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383500/extras/5dc89dc68162e3f81d217562c4927d67.webm?t=1597647957\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383500/extras/4343042cc6034b346454b41000566c6a.poster.avif?t=1597647957\" width=71 height=103 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383500/extras/4343042cc6034b346454b41000566c6a.webm?t=1597647957\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383500/extras/20eec7a24f8483c0a69c770ca3d54d31.poster.avif?t=1597647957\" width=71 height=103 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383500/extras/20eec7a24f8483c0a69c770ca3d54d31.webm?t=1597647957\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "《客栈江湖》，带着江湖风味的经营类游戏，而你扮演一名在江湖中寂寂无名的客栈掌柜。<br>你需要不断的接待客人，获取铜钱，派临时雇员去四处为你探索收集食谱与食材。在夜晚培养你的厨师，研究与学习菜谱，提升客栈在江湖中的名声，吸引更多的客人到来。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383500/extras/1e69c84e829a5fb2545eef1e4fee8e5f.poster.avif?t=1597647957\" width=71 height=103 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383500/extras/1e69c84e829a5fb2545eef1e4fee8e5f.webm?t=1597647957\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>初期只是一个小客栈，当拥有足够的金钱和名声时，可以对客栈进行升级，获得更多的座位以及厨师岗位。通过固定时间段的比赛，最终成为名扬四海的客栈。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383500/extras/5dc89dc68162e3f81d217562c4927d67.poster.avif?t=1597647957\" width=71 height=103 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383500/extras/5dc89dc68162e3f81d217562c4927d67.webm?t=1597647957\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383500/extras/4343042cc6034b346454b41000566c6a.poster.avif?t=1597647957\" width=71 height=103 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383500/extras/4343042cc6034b346454b41000566c6a.webm?t=1597647957\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383500/extras/20eec7a24f8483c0a69c770ca3d54d31.poster.avif?t=1597647957\" width=71 height=103 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_ite